OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fmostly sunny evening. Lengthy clear
OL,7,Fspells overnight will allow areas of
OL,8,Ffog and low cloud to develop, with
OL,9,Ffrost possible especially in prone
OL,10,Frural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA chilly start once again,
OL,13,Fwith early frost, fog and low cloud
OL,14,Fsoon clearing to leave another dry and
OL,15,Fsunny day. Remaining cooler near
OL,16,Fcoasts, although coastal winds easing
OL,17,Fsomewhat.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
