OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,6,Fdry during this period, with sunny
OL,7,Fspells likely. Risk of overnight fog
OL,8,Fand frost. Often cool near coasts, but
OL,9,Fwarm inland. Breezy along coasts on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
